{"tid":1110641,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"發現我隻貓好似生貓癬","createTime":"2019-04-16T15:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T19:15:21.000Z","uid":125805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6528d7e3c5dad9a486a05e7ef063aecef6ee5c","tid":1110641,"uid":125805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩幫佢梳毛，唔知係咪梳得太大力<br />\n梳完之後我發現佢無左一忽仔毛<br />\n但梳梗個陣佢又無掙扎叫個啲<br />\n睇翻梳出黎個汁毛都好正常<br />\n之後我就上網睇發現同貓癬好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下各位巴絲呢啲係咪貓癬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9322fda5073dcfd588164c3a5d1f8549670e3381","tid":1110641,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n<br />\n快啲全屋大清潔+消毒<br />\n<br />\n買癬患清俾佢食<br />\n同埋用麻辣洗幫佢沖一次涼<br />\n<br />\n我之前啲貓都有，沖完再食個幾星期癬患清就冇事"},{"pid":"05ee8447fa646c297afe90233b2824f599a51d1a","tid":1110641,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"我隻貓試過,開頭以為佢hi到AA膠水, 硬塊+甩毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住知道係貓癬<br />\n將個位剃左毛, 噴藥水, 幾日好返<br />\n不過生過癬唔會斷尾, 有次同一位置復發, 不過範圍好細, 發現得早, 再噴藥抑制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141209e90d8ca1902a63ca66b5eb82562ed1ed44","tid":1110641,"uid":125805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078db43b0491672bb8d1701bc38c50b37db32215","tid":1110641,"uid":137217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仲聽上面啲on9講自己搞<br />\n有可能係真菌感染"},{"pid":"1872c730535cc21fe98347e060ac998494fca763","tid":1110641,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"078db43b